direction: down

Driver: **Driver agent**

Delegate: **Delegated worker**
(automation / sub-agent)

Artifacts: **Artifacts**
(plan/research logs,
patch plan,
file pointers)

Review: **Review gate**
(compress + sanity check)

Integrate: **Integrate**
(edit code/docs)

Verify: **Verify**
(precommit/tests)

Persist: **Persist context**
(MEMORY/STATUS/RELEASES)

Driver -> Delegate: narrow mechanical task
Delegate -> Artifacts: compressed handback
Artifacts -> Review
Review -> Integrate
Integrate -> Verify
Verify -> Persist
Persist -> Driver: next slice
